</a>
<h2 class="bold font-l">Mickey Mouse</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Pete claims he wouldn't dream of cheating while crossing his fingers, to symbolize he's lying. </p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="alt-titles section section-fact">
<h3>
<strong>Alternative Title(s):</strong>
<span>Lying Crossed Fingers</span>, <span>Cross My Fingers And Hope To Lie</span> </h3>
</div>
